profile:
Studio Linea is an Oakville-based company providing professional home staging and redesigning services to homeowners, realtors and home builders.
Studio Linea is a certified, registered home stagers company with the Real Estate Staging Association. It offers a dynamic and competitive edge to the art of home-staging.We offer professional services dedicated to assist homeowners in preparing their house for sale during this delicate time. Our commitment and passion to any project, small or large scale, has always been recognized by referrals and recommendations.
service_area: Hamilton, Burlington, Oakville, Mississauga, Etobicoke, Toronto.
services: Consultation, space planning colour scheme,floor plan, neutralizing, decluttering, storage, painting, minor repairs.
specialities: Vacant and lived in homes, condos, townhouses.
diplomas: Haverhill Institute of Staging and Design.Marketing/economic degree.
licenses: Master Business Licence as part of Ontario  business program-Professional Home Stager Certification
memberships: RESA- VP Public Relation for Real Estate Staging Association-  IDRC- member of Interior Decor Res
project_rate: Consultation will provide estimate for the scope.
project_minimum: Every situation is different and every home is unique. Contact me for a consultation
